WEBVTT

00:07.257 --> 00:08.509
Well, it's the
beginnings of a pattern.

00:08.675 --> 00:09.847
<i>And Shirley attacked</i>

00:10.010 --> 00:11.307
<i>and attempted
to kill her mother.</i>

00:11.470 --> 00:12.312
<i>We don't see that happen.</i>

00:12.471 --> 00:13.472
<i>It's psychotic.</i>

00:13.639 --> 00:15.562
We're only looking
for a body now.

00:15.724 --> 00:18.102
<i>The toxins
accumulate in apex predators.</i>

00:18.268 --> 00:20.362
<i>Shirley Allerdyce
was an apex predator.</i>

00:20.521 --> 00:22.239
Frank! Oh, my God.

00:22.397 --> 00:24.491
If I don't get the truth,
they'll take Liam.

00:24.650 --> 00:27.073
It's not that I can't
forgive you. It's that

00:27.236 --> 00:28.783
<i>you're not my man anymore.</i>

00:28.946 --> 00:30.619
But I didn't do it for gain,

00:30.781 --> 00:33.534
I didn't do it for advantage.

00:33.700 --> 00:36.579
I did it out of love.

00:36.745 --> 00:38.793
Who was there
when Bill Pettigrew died?

00:38.956 --> 00:40.128
Come on, Henry.

00:40.290 --> 00:41.917
You'll have to accept that

00:42.084 --> 00:44.428
<i>there's some things
we'll never understand.</i>

00:44.586 --> 00:47.089
<i>When's Henry coming back?
I'd like to talk to him.</i>

00:47.256 --> 00:49.850
<i>He's not coming back, is he?</i>

