Hey, Frank.
How are you?

47:54.663 --> 47:56.165
I don't think
my dad's coming home.

47:56.332 --> 47:59.211
<i>I think my he's dead.</i>

47:59.377 --> 48:01.471
<i>It's not a new hotel we need.
It's a...</i>

